OL,6,FThe interim findings of Operation
OL,7,FKenova were revealed after an
OL,8,Finvestigation lasting seven years and
OL,9,Fcosting approximately #40 million.
OL,11,FKenova has probed the activities of
OL,12,Fthe agent Stakeknife within the
OL,13,FProvisional IRA. He has not been
OL,14,Fidentified in the report, however, the
OL,15,Freport authors have called on the
OL,16,Fgovernment to reveal his identity and
OL,17,Fexpect it to do so in order that it be
OL,18,Fincluded in the final Kenova report.
