OL,3,CArmy double agent operations within
OL,4,CIRA cost lives, report finds
OL,6,FInvestigators examined 101 killings
OL,7,Fand abductions linked to the IRA unit
OL,8,Fresponsible for interrogating and
OL,9,Ftorturing people suspected of passing
OL,10,Finformation to the security forces
OL,11,Fduring the conflict.
OL,13,FStakeknife was part of the terror
OL,14,Fgroup's internal security unit - known
OL,15,Fas the 'nutting squad'. and Kenova
OL,16,Fexamined crimes such as murder and
OL,17,Ftorture, and the role played by the
OL,18,Fsecurity services, including MI5.
