OL,3,CArmy double agent operations within
OL,4,CIRA cost lives, report finds
OL,6,FSome 32 people, including former
OL,7,Fpolice, former military personnel and
OL,8,Fpeople linked with the IRA, were
OL,9,Fconsidered for prosecution on a range
OL,10,Fof charges from murder and abduction
OL,11,Fto misconduct in public office and
OL,12,Fperjury.
OL,14,FHowever, the PPS found there was
OL,15,Finsufficient evidence to pursue cases.
OL,17,FThe Operation Kenova report stops
OL,18,Fshort of confirming Scappaticci as
OL,19,FStakeknife.
