OL,6,FHowever, it says that the Kenova team
OL,7,Fhad passed "strong evidence of very
OL,8,Fserious criminality" by Scappaticci to
OL,9,Fprosecutors in Northern Ireland prior
OL,10,Fto his death.
OL,12,FThe report also dismisses rumours that
OL,13,FScappaticci might still be alive.
OL,15,FAmong 10 recommendations in the 208
OL,16,Fpage report, is a call for the UK
OL,17,Fauthorities to review the application
OL,18,Fof the Neither Confirm Nor Deny policy
OL,19,F(NCND) that currently prevents the
OL,20,Fidentification of agents involved in
OL,21,Fmany historical Troubles cases.
