OL,6,F"In reality the claims are inherently
OL,7,Fimplausible and should ring alarm
OL,8,Fbells: any serious security and
OL,9,Fintelligence professional hearing an
OL,10,Fagent being likened to 'the goose that
OL,11,Flaid the golden eggs', as Stakeknife
OL,12,Fwas, should be on alert because the
OL,13,Fcomparison is rooted in fables and
OL,14,Ffairy tales," he said.
